  "detailed_description": "Space Commander 9 is a modern 3D space shooter game that puts you in the seat of a space ship with orders to defend the human race against the alien invasion. <br />\r\nBuild and manage your space arsenal, and defend your world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMain Features:<br />\r\n•\tSpace Shipyard - Where Player can unlock new spaceships.<br />\r\n•\tWeapon Station - Where Player can upgrade ship system, purchase and mount new weapons and create his own preferable Spaceship design.<br />\r\n•\tCommander Perks - where player can train his commander.<br />\r\n•\tEarn credits to purchase, research to unlock & upgrade new ships and ship modules, allowing you to better defend your ship and your planet.",
